description: It's a new team and direction for the Titans! Deathstroke and his mercenary team including Cheshire, Tattooed Man and other surprise members burst out of BRIGHTEST DAY #0! Get in on the ground floor here as the team is hired to assassinate The Atom! And for this team, failure is not an option!
name: The Best Laid Plans

description: Dante has reached the end of his journey. But does he arrive a conquering hero to save the soul of his beloved Beatrice? Or a damned, corrupted shadow of himself, changed forever by his ordeal in the Inferno?
name: Defeat

description: Finally, Mischa faces the man who destroyed her. But will Dedalus kill Eddie? Will Harold Furey regret mutilating Limm? Will the secret of Sandy's past be revealed? Look for hubris, catharsis and more than a little irony in "Agnorosis," the final episode of GREEK STREET: BOOK TWO.
name: Book Two: Cassandra Complex, Part Six: Agnorosis

description: TEAM-UP WITH CAPTAIN BRITAIN - Special Relationship Cor Blimey guv'nor and, indeed, luv a duck. The fabled missing weapons haul of Captain Britain's old enemy Slaymaster has finally been discovered, which sends Deadpool, and every other mercenary with air miles to cash in, to jolly old England in pursuit of a VERY large payday. But Captain Britain isn't just going to let the deadly Slaymaster tech hit the open market. That just wouldn't be cricket.
name: Guest Starring Captain Britain

description:
Andromeda and Lucien battle Voivodul, the evil Dayak sorcerer-god.

Lucien breaks through the very first part of this story, beating back the forces which is before him. Andromeda accompanies him and watches as he slashes and rips through flesh. It is a very short story giving some information on what is in store for the story arc.

Cover Price: Free

Format: Color; Standard Comic Issue; 16 pages
name: Wizard 0

description: When the Red Skull infiltrates the United States government, he authorizes a biological weapon to be released from the peaks of Mount Rushmore, and it is up the Avengers to contain it! Under the direction of creators Geoff Johns and Olivier Coipel, the Avengers face a threat unlike any they've ever faced, then they take on the Red Skull himself! Collecting AVENGERS (1998) #65-70.
name: Avengers: Red Zone

description: The Dragon War comes its brutal, bloody end!
name: Dragon War, Part Six - Battlefront

description: Angry and dangerous loners are famed for keeping journals, and Frank Castle is no exception! The Punisher confronts deadly enemies from both war and peacetime, but a vacation in Africa introduces him to a far different legacy of the past: dinosaurs! But the wild man waiting to throw down on him is no throwback. It's Wolverine! Guns vs. claws for the historic first time! Guest-starring Daredevil! Collecting PUNISHER WAR JOURNAL #1-8.
name: Volume 1

description: Can one man stand against an army fueled by pure hate? With recent tragedies still rattling in his head, Frank Castle finds himself tied to a fencepost with barbed wire, watching what may be his last sunrise. Somewhere along the U.S./Mexico border, a super-militia bent on igniting a race war has been killing scores of innocent people. By the time the last shot is fired and the last body falls, you'll have met the modern incarnation of the Hate Monger and seen an all-new look for the Punisher. Meanwhile, in Washington DC, someone wants to have words with Frank about his recent patriotic costume change: the Winter Soldier himself, Bucky Barnes! Collecting PUNISHER WAR JOURNAL #5-11.
name: Volume 2

volume.name: Punisher War Journal: Goin' Out West

description: With G.I. Joe captured and held prisoner, Major Bludd puts his master plan into action… and makes sure that the Joes take the fall!
